memberdef.name: DISALLOW_COPY_AND_ASSIGN
memberdef.initializer: classname(const classname &) = delete; \ classname &operator=(const classname &) = delete;

memberdef.name: DECLARE_SINGLETON
memberdef.initializer: public: \ static classname *Instance(bool create_if_needed = true) { \ static classname *instance = nullptr; \ if (!instance && create_if_needed) { \ static std::once_flag flag; \ std::call_once(flag, \ [&] { instance = new (std::nothrow) classname(); }); \ } \ return instance; \ } \ \ static void CleanUp() { \ auto instance = Instance(false); \ if (instance != nullptr) { \ CallShutdown(instance); \ } \ } \ \ private: \ classname(); \ DISALLOW_COPY_AND_ASSIGN(classname)
